&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own execution for your team end-to-end: delivery, quality bar, scope trade-offs, and the decisions that get things shipped without accumulating technical debt&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Embed AI tooling into how your team builds as a default, not a suggestion, identifying where it accelerates development cycles, improves code quality, and removes bottlenecks that previously required human intervention&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect the layer of AI-powered systems and tooling that makes your team disproportionately productive, not just feature-shipping, but building the automation that multiplies output&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Product and Design from early strategy through production, bringing engineering perspective into the room before decisions are made&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to technical direction for your area: surface platform needs and scaling challenges early, and help your team make good architectural calls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop your team: invest in its growth, stretch the high-potential, and build a team where people get better because of working there&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with recruiting to hire strong engineers, hold a high bar on every candidate, and build a team culture that retains them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
